@startuml

[*] --> Order
state Order <<initial>>
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state Service
state OutOfService
state Removed

Order --> Arrival : plane arrives
Arrival --> Preparation : upon arrival
Preparation --> [choose(Condition, Schedule, MaintenanceNeeded)]
Condition --> Operations : scheduled flights
Condition --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Service : after checking and servicing
Service --> Preparation : ready for operations

Operations --> [choose(ScheduledFlights, MaintenanceNeeded)]
ScheduledFlights --> Operations
MaintenanceNeeded --> Maintenance

Maintenance --> Service
Service --> Preparation

Preparation --> OutOfService : no longer available for use
OutOfService --> Removed : permanently withdrawn from service

@enduml
